name: r-catnet
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.15.7" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-catnet
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/catnet_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/catnet/catnet_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0f09e439e66fc08108582d63359be211076080a073c873cea5b748096682b804

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}      # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('catnet')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('catnet')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=catnet
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: 'Structure learning and parameter estimation of discrete Bayesian networks using likelihood-based criteria.  Exhaustive search for fixed node orders and
    stochastic search of optimal orders via simulated annealing algorithm are implemented.  '
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r

# Package: catnet
# Title: Categorical Bayesian Network Inference
# Version: 1.15.5
# Author: Nikolay Balov, Peter Salzman
# Description: Structure learning and parameter estimation of discrete Bayesian networks using likelihood-based criteria.  Exhaustive search for fixed node orders and stochastic search of optimal orders via simulated annealing algorithm are implemented.
# Maintainer: Nikolay Balov <nhbalov@gmail.com>
